	keywords = {goals, system, governance, SDGs},
	pages = {176--187},
	annote = {This is an important paper for our "Goals" section, partly because of its analytical description of the dog's breakfast of the SDGs, but also because of the interesting route by which he shows "Well-being" to be a "core goal", and sustainable PC systems a powerful point of leverage on most all of the SDGs.  (BC: ends / means).
