I love her idea of critical realism.
 
},
	annote = {The paper describes the gap between policy intentions and outcomes. It emphasizes the need for multi-level approaches that relate policy decisions at national and international level with decisions of local resource users. Analyses of decentralized natural resource policies need to go beyond the understanding of how the decisions of local communities are affected by centrally designed policies. Exploring the gaps between rhetoric and outcomes requires considering the multiple governance tiers through which policies are negotiated and implemented. 
